{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018wqj7ZjSN8gvx9bRzjeDe5","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect. I now have the exact definitions. Here's what I found:\n\n## CloseCallPhase Variants\n\nFrom `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs` (lines 11-19):\n\n```rust\n#[derive(AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Debug, InitSpace)]\npub enum CloseCallPhase {\n    /// Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle).\n    Open,\n    /// Outcome determined, payouts distributed.\n    Settled,\n    /// All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close).\n    Refunded,\n}\n```\n\n**Variants:**\n- `Open` — Round is open for bets (first 30s of candle)\n- `Settled` — Outcome determined, payouts distributed\n- `Refunded` — All bets refunded (invalid round, timeout, or force close)\n\n## Outcome Variants\n\nFrom `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/closecall/src/state.rs` (lines 21-28):\n\n```rust\n#[derive(AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize, Clone, Copy, PartialEq, Eq, Debug, InitSpace)]\npub enum Outcome {\n    Pending,\n    Green,\n    Red,\n    Refund,\n}\n```\n\n**Variants:**\n- `Pending` — No outcome yet\n- `Green` — Green (bull) side won\n- `Red` — Red (bear) side won\n- `Refund` — Round refunded\n\n## TypeScript Mapping\n\nThe generated TypeScript types in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/anchor-client/src/closecall.ts` match exactly (camelCase):\n\n- `closeCallPhase` enum: `open`, `settled`, `refunded`\n- `outcome` enum: `pending`, `green`, `red`, `refund`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a235050fbf0c6988b (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 43631\ntool_uses: 3\nduration_ms: 7313</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5daa2fb-13cd-4249-820b-ad6ea49cbd9b","uuid":"0979c106-ecd4-4de1-a39e-b38bc0b8f232","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prom