{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018VZUpFWDfsBM5qJv9yZcZu","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete picture. Let me compile the comprehensive report for you.\n\n---\n\n## Close-Call Frontend Feature — Complete Analysis\n\nI've explored the entire close-call feature directory and read all files. Here's what you need to know:\n\n### Directory Structure\n```\nsources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/\n├── components/            (6 components)\n├── context/              (1 context provider)\n├── data/                 (1 JSON candle data file)\n├── hooks/                (1 index re-export)\n├── utils/                (3 utility modules)\n├── types.ts              (Central type definitions)\n├── index.ts              (Public API)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Core Types (`types.ts`)\n\n**Key type exports:**\n\n| Type | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `BetSide` | Union: `\"green\" \\| \"red\"` — player's side selection |\n| `RoundPhase` | Union: `\"betting\" \\| \"locked\" \\| \"resolving\" \\| \"complete\"` — state machine |\n| `CandleOutcome` | Union: `\"green\" \\| \"red\" \\| \"doji\"` — candle result |\n| `Candle` | OHLC data with `open/high/low/close` + `openTime/closeTime` (Unix ms) |\n| `PlayerBet` | Single player bet: `address, side, amount ($), timestamp, displayName?` |\n| `PoolState` | Aggregated pool: `greenPool, redPool, totalPool, playerCount, greenBets[], redBets[]` |\n| `Round` | Complete round data: id, phase, pool, timing, targetCandleTime, outcome, carryover, fairness data, winners, payouts |\n| `UserRoundHistory` | Player's view of a completed round: `round, userBet, payout, won` |\n| `CloseCallContextValue` | Context API shape (see below) |\n\n**Key constants:**\n- `DEFAULT_BET_AMOUNT = 0.5`\n- `MIN_BET_AMOUNT = 0.1`\n- `MAX_BET_AMOUNT = 1000`\n- `PLATFORM_FEE_BPS = 300` (3%)\n- `PLATFORM_FEE = 0.03`\n- `DOJI_THRESHOLD_BPS = 1` (0.01% close-to-open = doji)\n- `CANDLE_DURATION_MS = 60000` (adjustable by `CANDLE_SPEED_MULTIPLIER`)\n- `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 10000` (first 10 seconds)\n- `SIDE_COLORS = { green: \"#45b058\", red: \"#dc3545\", doji: \"#f0b820\" }`\n\n---\n\n## Context API (`CloseCallContext.tsx`)\n\n**Provider:** `<CloseCallProvider>` — wraps the game content\n\n**Hook:** `useCloseCall()` returns `CloseCallContextValue` with:\n\n### State\n- `currentRound: Round | null` — the active round players bet on\n- `completedRound: Round | null` — most recent finished round (for result display)\n- `recentCandles: Candle[]` — last 15 completed candles + current forming candle\n- `currentPrice: number` — interpolated price during the forming candle\n- `candleProgress: number` — 0-1 progress through current candle\n- `carryoverJackpot: number` — DOJI carryover amount to next round\n- `userHistory: UserRoundHistory[]` — all past rounds for the connected address\n- `userBet: PlayerBet | null` — player's bet in current round (if any)\n- `pendingAmount: number` — bet amount typed by user\n- `pendingSide: BetSide | null` — selected green/red (null if not chosen)\n- `loading: boolean` — game init\n- `placingBet: boolean` — transaction in progress\n- `claiming: boolean` — claim payout in progress\n\n### Actions\n- `setPendingAmount(amount: number)` — update input bet amount\n- `setPendingSide(side: BetSide | null)` — select green/red\n- `placeBet(side?: BetSide)` — submit bet with optional side override\n- `adjustBetAmount(adjustment: \"half\" | \"double\" | \"max\")` — quick buttons\n- `claimPayout()` — claim winnings (async, not auto)\n- `clearCompletedRound()` — dismiss result overlay\n- `refreshRound()` — manually fetch round state\n- `potentialPayout: number` — calculated payout if user's pending bet wins\n- `userOdds: number` — user's % share of their chosen pool\n\n---\n\n## Components\n\n### `CandlestickChart.tsx`\n- Uses **lightweight-charts** library for candlestick visualization\n- Renders 5 history candles (muted colors) + current forming candle (vibrant green/red)\n- Displays current price, O/H/L values in a price panel\n- Progress bar shows betting window (white, 10s) vs. locked window (gray, 50s)\n- Countdown label: \"BETTING OPEN • Xs to bet\" or \"BETTING LOCKED • Candle Close in Xs\"\n- **Key logic:** Interpolates price within the forming candle; high/low update as price ticks\n\n### `BetAmountInput.tsx`\n- Text input field (`inputMode=\"decimal\"`)\n- Three quick-adjust buttons: ½, 2x, MAX\n- Validates on blur: clamps to `[MIN, MAX]`, resets to MIN if invalid\n- Displays min/max range at bottom\n- Props: `value, onChange, onAdjust, disabled, maxAmount`\n\n### `SideSelector.tsx`\n- Two large buttons: GREEN and RED\n- Shows \"Joining...\" text while `placingBet=true`\n- Disables opposite side during transaction\n- Uses CSS variables for side colors\n- Props: `selectedSide, onSelect, disabled, placingBet`\n\n### `PoolDistribution.tsx`\n- **Pool breakdown:** Pie chart showing green% vs. red% split\n- **Pool stats:** Green/Red amounts and odds multipliers (~Xx format)\n- **Prize pool:** Bold centered display of total + optional \"+$X jackpot\" banner\n- **User bet section** (if player has bet): \n  - Joined GREEN/RED (colored)\n  - Your Amount\n  - Potential Payout (with profit calculated)\n  - **Win/Loss animations:** Stars + coins for wins, heartbreak emoji for losses\n- Props: `pool, carryoverAmount, userBet, potentialPayout, roundOutcome, isRoundComplete`\n\n### `ActiveBetView.tsx`\n- Shows user's active bet details\n- Phase text: \"Waiting for candle...\" → \"Bets locked...\" → \"Determining outcome...\" → \"Round complete\"\n- Displays: stake, share of pool (%), potential win, multiplier\n- Note: \"Your odds may change as more bets come in\" (betting phase)\n- Note: \"Odds are now locked. Good luck!\" (locked phase)\n- Props: `round, userBet`\n\n### `RoundResultOverlay.tsx`\n- Modal overlay that auto-displays when round completes\n- Shows outcome candle visualization (colored box)\n- Result text: \"YOU WON!\" / \"YOU LOST\" / \"DOJI - No Winner!\"\n- Candle details: Open/Close/Change\n- Fairness data: Round ID (last 12 chars), Server Seed (truncated, only shown if revealed)\n- Win/Loss animations (same as PoolDistribution)\n- Auto-closes after 5 seconds or user clicks \"Continue\"\n- Props: `round, userBet, onClose`\n\n---\n\n## Utilities\n\n### `payout-calculator.ts`\n\n**Key functions:**\n\n| Function | Returns | Purpose |\n|----------|---------|---------|\n| `determineOutcome(candle)` | `CandleOutcome` | Compare close vs. open; threshold at 0.01% = doji |\n| `calculatePayouts(pool, outcome, carryover)` | `PayoutResult` | Distribute net pool to winners; handle doji carryover |\n| `calculatePotentialPayout(betAmount, side, pool, carryover)` | `number` | Preview payout if user's pending bet wins |\n| `calculateOddsMultiplier(side, pool, carryover)` | `number` | How much $1 would win |\n| `calculatePoolDistribution(pool)` | `{green%, red%}` | Pool split for display |\n| `formatAmount / formatUsd` | `string` | Display formatting |\n\n**Formula:**\n```\ntotalPool = greenPool + redPool + carryover\nnetPool = totalPool × 0.97 (3% fee)\nplayerPayout = (playerBet / winningPool) × netPool\n```\n\n**DOJI handling:** If outcome is \"doji\" → no winners, entire pool (minus 3% fee) carries to next round.\n\n### `mock-simulation.ts`\n\n**Game state store:**\n- `currentRound` — actively betting round\n- `completedRound` — most recent finished round\n- `roundHistory` — archive of all rounds\n- `userHistory` — per-address bet history (Map)\n- `carryoverAmount` — DOJI carryover pool\n- `replayEngine` — candle playback engine\n\n**Key functions:**\n\n| Function | Purpose |\n|----------|---------|\n| `initializeGame()` | Start game, hook replay engine callbacks |\n| `placeBet(address, side, amount)` | Submit a bet; validates amount, phase, duplication |\n| `scheduleMockBets()` | Generate 3-7 random NPC bets during betting window |\n| `subscribeToRound(callback)` | Listen for round changes |\n| `subscribeToCompletedRound(callback)` | Listen for round completion (result display) |\n| `getCurrentRound()` | Getter |\n| `getRecentCandles(count)` | Get last N completed candles |\n| `getCurrentCandle()` | Getter for forming candle |\n| `getCandleProgress()` | 0-1 progress through candle |\n| `getCarryoverAmount()` | Getter |\n| `isGameInitialized()` | Getter |\n\n**Round lifecycle (internal state machine):**\n1. `onCandleStart`: Create new round, start betting\n2. `onCandleComplete`: Resolve outcome, calculate payouts, emit events\n3. `onPriceTick`: Poll for betting window lock (10s timeout)\n\n**Event emissions:**\n- `emitWagerPlaced()` → RNG chest drop checks\n- `emitCloseCallComplete()` → Boss Raid integration\n- `emitCloseCallResults()` → Player Profile XP/stats tracking\n\n### `candle-replay.ts`\n\n**`CandleReplayEngine` class:**\n\nReplays bundled BTC candle JSON as \"live\" data for mock mode.\n\n**Key methods:**\n- `start(callbacks)` — Begin replay with event hooks\n- `stop()` — Stop replay\n- `tick()` — Internal: interpolate price, check for candle completion\n- `interpolatePrice(candle, progress)` — Realistic movement within candle (open → high/low → close)\n- `getCurrentCandle()` — Getter\n- `getRecentCandles(count)` — History for chart\n- `getCandlesUpToCurrent(count)` — Completed candles + current\n- `getProgress()` — 0-1 progress\n- `getTimeRemaining()` — ms until candle closes\n\n**Callbacks (from mock-simulation.ts):**\n- `onCandleStart(candle, index)` → create round\n- `onCandleComplete(candle)` → resolve round\n- `onPriceTick(price, progress, candle)` → update UI price/progress\n\n---\n\n## Data (`btc-candles.json`)\n\n150 simulated BTC/USD 1-minute candles. Each candle has:\n```json\n{\n  \"open\": 96150.00,\n  \"high\": 96185.50,\n  \"low\": 96120.00,\n  \"close\": 96175.25,\n  \"openTime\": 1706400000000,\n  \"closeTime\": 1706400059999\n}\n```\n\nWrapped in:\n```json\n{\n  \"metadata\": { \"asset\": \"BTC\", \"interval\": \"1m\", \"source\": \"generated\", \"count\": 150 },\n  \"candles\": [...]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## External Integration (`CloseCallPage.tsx`)\n\n**Located at:** `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CloseCallPage.tsx`\n\n**Imports from close-call:**\n- `CloseCallProvider, useCloseCall` — context\n- `CandlestickChart, BetAmountInput, SideSelector, PoolDistribution` — components\n- `SIDE_COLORS` — constants\n- Types: `UserRoundHistory, BetSide`\n\n**Page structure:**\n- Wraps content in `<CloseCallProvider>`\n- Sidebar:\n  - Jackpot banner (carryover display)\n  - Bet amount input\n  - Side selector (green/red buttons)\n  - Pool distribution bar\n  - Auto-payout message for winners\n  - Fairness info (round ID, seed hash)\n- Main:\n  - Result banner (after round completes)\n  - Chart description\n  - Candlestick chart\n- Modals:\n  - History detail modal (click a past round)\n\n**Usage of context:**\n- Reads: `currentRound, completedRound, recentCandles, currentPrice, candleProgress, userHistory, carryoverJackpot, pendingAmount, pendingSide, userBet, loading, placingBet`\n- Calls: `setPendingAmount, setPendingSide, placeBet, adjustBetAmount, clearCompletedRound`\n- Computes: `potentialPayout`\n- Converts history to UI format (HistoryEntry for shared @rng-utopia/ui)\n\n---\n\n## Key Data Flows\n\n### Betting Flow\n```\nUser types amount → setPendingAmount()\nUser clicks GREEN/RED → setPendingSide() + placeBet(side)\n  → mock-simulation.placeBet() validates + adds to round.pool\n  → round state emitted via subscribeToRound()\n  → context updates currentRound, userBet\n  → UI shows: \"Joined GREEN\", amount, potential payout, odds\n```\n\n### Outcome Flow\n```\ncandle-replay engine completes candle → onCandleComplete()\n  → mock-simulation.resolveRound()\n    → determineOutcome(resultCandle) [compare close vs. open]\n    → calculatePayouts(pool, outcome)\n    → reveal serverSeed + blockHash\n    → update userHistory for all bettors\n    → emit events (Boss Raid, Player Profile)\n  → notifyCompletedListeners()\n    → context.setCompletedRound()\n    → RoundResultOverlay displays result\n    → Auto-dismiss after 5s or user click\n```\n\n### Display Updates\n```\nContext-level polling every 100ms:\n  → getCurrentCandle()\n  → getCandleProgress()\n  → interpolatePrice() for display\n  → setCurrentPrice(), setCandleProgress()\n  → chart re-renders\n  → progress bar updates\n  → countdown updates\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary of What Imports What\n\n**Files that import from `types.ts`:**\n- All components, context, utils, and the main page\n- Re-exported via `/index.ts` for external consumers\n\n**Files that import from `mock-simulation.ts`:**\n- `CloseCallContext.tsx` — lifecycle management (initializeGame, subscriptions, getters)\n- `RoundResultOverlay.tsx` — uses types only\n- `payout-calculator.ts` — uses `calculatePayouts, determineOutcome`\n\n**Files that import from `payout-calculator.ts`:**\n- `mock-simulation.ts` — calculate payouts after outcome\n- `CloseCallContext.tsx` — `calculatePotentialPayout` for preview\n- `PoolDistribution.tsx` (indirectly via types) — odds calculation\n\n**Files that import from `candle-replay.ts`:**\n- `mock-simulation.ts` — hooks into replay engine lifecycle\n\n---\n\nThis feature is a complete, self-contained pari-mutuel prediction game with mock replay data. All types flow through the context, all game logic lives in utils, and components are presentation-only."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a96054d48851d6fb2 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 76349\ntool_uses: 21\nduration_ms: 66506</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5daa2fb-13cd-4249-820b-ad6ea49cbd9b","uuid":"9962f9ca-6921-4e34-a53f-f0eb8f0c4f8c","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the close-call frontend feature directory. I need to understand:\n\n1. The full contents of `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts`\